snippet.title: What is Patch Quest?
snippet.description:
The Patch Quest Public Beta can be played for free via Discord. Just visit the #public-beta channel of the PQ server: 
▶https://discord.gg/patchquest

You can also wishlist Patch Quest on Steam: 
▶ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1347970/Patch_Quest/

And you can follow development on Twitter, too: 
▶ https://twitter.com/PatchQuest
